Text: You always for your help in translation into English. Greetings.
Thank you so much! works great!

Contains trojan Buzus. I'm not a noob, I know that 90% of virus alerts on TPB are false alarms, e.g. due to packers or altered file signatures being detected as suspicious. But this is an actual trojan infection, I've run it in a virtual machine to confirm.

Shame this has come from a green skull uploader, usually we can trust them to screen their uploads before posting the to TPB.
